      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried the walking foot and it helped a little but it's still not perfect. there are just these weird little tugs and snags happening every few inches. it's almost like something is snagging the thread from underneath or just unevenly grabbing the material as it goes through. is there anything else that could cause those tiny, irregular pulls?",
